{"id":63338,"type":1,"name":"Do Androids Dream of Electric Sheep?","name_cn":"仿生人会梦见电子羊吗？","date":"","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/a7/fa/63338_NXr0V.jpg","rating":{"rank":218,"total":94,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":0,"6":3,"7":7,"8":35,"9":28,"10":20},"score":8.5},"summary":"        故事发生在未来的1992年。Rick Deckard是为旧金山警察局抓逃亡机器人领赏金的“赏金猎人”（Bounty Hunter）。他早上照旧装作喂自己的电子羊，以免被邻居发现他原来的活羊已死而丢脸。同时,他的妻子在家里靠“同情箱”和“情绪器官”控制下打发时光。\r\n        Deckard在警署获悉：高级猎人Dave Holden被一个最新型号的Nexus-6型机器人重伤。Deckard 受命在旧金山地区搜寻剩下的六个同类机器人。他的顶头上司让他先去西雅图地区拜访该型号机器人的制造者--罗森公司--总部，去确认辨别人与机器人的Voigt-Kampff测试对Nexus-6型仍然有效。Deckard在总部遇到了自称是公司创始人之女的拉切尔·罗森，自荐做第一个测试对象。老罗森告诉Deckard说拉切尔有精神分裂症，但后来Deckard凭试验发现她其实是Nexus-6型机器人。Voigt-Kampff测试证明仍然有效，然而Deckard对人与机器人的差距有了更多的疑问......","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>仿生人会梦见电子羊吗？</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/34111\">Philip K. Dick</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span>Doubleday</li><li><span>发售日: </span>1968</li><li><span>页数: </span>210</li>","collection":{"on_hold":5,"dropped":2,"wish":95,"collect":122,"doing":9},"tags":[{"name":"科幻","count":35},{"name":"小说","count":24},{"name":"赛博朋克","count":17},{"name":"欧美","count":9},{"name":"已完结小说","count":1},{"name":"神作","count":1},{"name":"SF","count":1},{"name":"小说改","count":1},{"name":"","count":""}],"staff":[{"id":34111,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/d2/d2/34111_prsn_0m6iM.jpg","name":"Philip K. Dick","desc":"作者"}],"relations":[{"id":29145,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/cf/9d/29145_N3NCM.jpg","title":"Blade Runner (1997)","type":"游戏","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/29145"},{"id":268235,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/2a/4f/268235_1LL3p.jpg","title":"Blade Runner (1985)","type":"游戏","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/268235"},{"id":443573,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/1b/9f/443573_nGT8N.jpg","title":"Blade Runner 2033: Labyrinth","type":"游戏","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/443573"},{"id":72819,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/67/6d/72819_ImsmP.jpg","title":"Blade Runner","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm